<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Login</title>

<!-- 기본 셋팅 상속 -->
<%- include('basic-set')%>
<link href="/public/login.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <div id="login">
    <div><h2 class="info-Container">Login</h2><br></div>
    <form action="/login" method="POST" name="loginFrm">
      <div id="loginFrm-container">
        <div class="mb-3" id="id-container">
          <label for="userId" class="form-label">ID</label>
          <input type="text" class="form-control" id="userId" name="userId">
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3" id="pw-container">
          <label for="userPw" class="form-label">Password</label>
          <input type="password" class="form-control" id="userPw" name="userPw">
        </div>
        <div id="btn-container">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="loginSubmit">Submit</button>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">Join</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
    <br>
    <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
      아이디 또는 비밀번호를 잘못입력했습니다.다시 확인해주세요.
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.0/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-Q6E9RHvbIyZFJoft+2mJbHaEWldlvI9IOYy5n3zV9zzTtmI3UksdQRVvoxMfooAo" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>